==Finnish== 
===Verb===
nussia

# ''(vulgar, With the object in the partitive case)'' To fuck, screw, have sex.
#: ''Sinähän et '''nussi''' mun siskoani!''
#: "You will not '''fuck''' my sister!"
# ''(vulgar, With the object in the genitive-accusative case)'' To steal, snatch, [[feck]].
#: ''Kuka vittu on '''nussinut''' mun lompakkoni?''
#: "Who the '''fuck''' has snatched my wallet?"

